HEADWORD: Hyperodontidae
<hw>Hyperodontidae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A natural family of
cetaceans comprising the beaked whales; in some, especially former,
classifications it included in the family
<fam>Physeteridae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Ziphiidae, family <fam>Ziphiidae</fam>, family
<fam>Hyperodontidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

